      "content": "idk if i even want to be \"gentle\" with myself. i just want the heaviness to stop. it's like i'm just going through the motions and for what? everything is just empty. i feel like i'm just waiting for something to happen, but i know nothing will. it would be so much easier if i just didn't have to carry this anymore.",
